      <body>
         <head>Japanese Lullaby</head>
         
         <lg>
            <l>Neneko, neneko, Ya!</l>
            <l>Sleep, my little one, sleep!</l>
            <l>As the bottomless pit of the ocean,</l>
            <l>So is my love so deep!</l>
         </lg>
         
         <lg>
            <l>Neneko, neneko, Ya!</l>
            <l>Sleep, my little one, sleep!</l>
            <l>As the unexplored vasts of Nirvanna,</l>
            <l>So is my love so deep.</l>
         </lg>
         
      </body>
